<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-system-font" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying System Font</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>System font is the font of Serna user interface: menus, toolbars, dialogs, tabs, etc. You can change the font, its style, size, script, and apply effects.</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>General tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>General tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-general-tab-system-font.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Choose font</uicontrol> button next to the <uicontrol>System font</uicontrol> field.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>In the <keyword>Select Font Dialog</keyword>, specify the font and click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>Select Font Dialog.</title>
            <image href="select-font-dialog.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Apply</uicontrol> button to apply the settings.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
